---
servings: 4
time: 30 min
---

= Preparation =

Peel and dice @potatoes{500%g} into small cubes.

Mince @garlic{3%cloves} finely.

= Cooking =

Heat @olive oil{2%tbsp} in a #large pan{} over medium heat.

Add the potatoes and cook for ~{15%minutes} until golden.

Add garlic and @salt{1%tsp} and @pepper{} to taste.

-- This is a comment
Cook for another ~{5%minutes} until fragrant.
